 is a Pan-African technology and business solutions firm dedicated to driving digital transformation and enterprise growth. We specialise in delivering high-impact, cost-effective solutions across six key divisions:</p><table class="cred-table" style="margin-top:14px"><tbody><tr><td>ICT Hardware</td><td>Certified HP, Dell, Lenovo, Samsung, Synology, APC, Canon hardware supply</td></tr><tr><td>PC Assembly</td><td>Custom desktop PCs for office and education — assembled, tested, deployed</td></tr><tr><td>Software Development</td><td>Enterprise applications, web systems, cloud infrastructure — ASP.NET Core, Blazor, PostgreSQL</td></tr><tr><td>Language Services</td><td>Translation, transcription, interpretation, subtitling — English, Portuguese, Chichewa, Swahili</td></tr><tr><td>Medical Supplies</td><td>Healthcare equipment, consumables, pharmaceuticals — sourced through verified SADC partners</td></tr><tr><td>Infrastructure</td><td>LAN/WAN design, server room setup, cloud migration, system integration</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="sh"><h2>Diplomatic Reference</h2></div><div class="cred-section"><h3>🏛️ High Commission of the Republic of Mozambique</h3><p>Lilongwe, February 2026</p><p style="margin-top:10px">The High Commission confirms that TechNexus, through its language services division TechNexus Scripts, has been providing professional language services to this Mission over a sustained period. Assignments have included commercial agreements, contracts, lease agreements and legal/administrative texts. The Mission commends TechNexus for high standards of professionalism, accuracy, reliability, and discretion.</p><p style="margin-top:10px;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--amber)">Full reference letter available on request. Additional references from private sector and corporate clients available upon request.</p></div><div class="sh"><h2>Compliance Framework</h2></div><div class="cred-section"><table class="cred-table"><tbody><tr><td>Procurement</td><td>MANePS registered. Engagements conducted within the Public Finance Management Act (2022) framework.</td></tr><tr><td>Language Services</td><td>HIPAA/GDPR-aware. NDA signed by all translators and transcribers. Encrypted data handling.</td></tr><tr><td>Medical Supplies</td><td>Sourced through verified wholesale partners across the SADC region.</td></tr><tr><td>Audit</td><td>Full audit trails maintained on every project and engagement.</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="sh" style="margin-top:48px"><h2>Contact Us</h2><p class="sd">Send us your enquiry. We respond within 24 hours.</p></div><div class="form-wrap"><form action="https://formsubmit.co/technexus_mw@proton.me" method="POST"><div class="form-grid"><div class="form-row"><label>Full Name *</label><input name="Full Name" placeholder="Your full name" required="" type="text"></div><div class="form-row"><label>Company / Organisation</label><input name="Company" placeholder="Company name (optional)" type="text"></div></div><div class="form-grid"><div class="form-row"><label>Email Address *</label><input name="Email" placeholder="your@email.com" required="" type="email"></div><div class="form-row"><label>Phone Number</label><input name="Phone" placeholder="+265 ..." type="tel"></div></div><div class="form-row"><label>Service of Interest</label><select name="Service"><option value="">— Select a service —</option><option value="ICT Hardware">ICT Hardware &amp; Equipment</option><option value="PC Assembly">Custom PC Assembly</option><option value="Software Development">Software Development</option><option value="Language Services">Language Services (TechNexus Scripts)</option><option value="Medical Supplies">Medical Supplies</option><option value="General Enquiry">General Enquiry</option></select></div><div class="form-row"><label>Your Enquiry *</label><textarea name="Message" placeholder="Describe your requirements, project scope, or question..." required=""></textarea></div><button class="btn-submit" type="submit">Send